.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:21:43.000Z","msg":"簽發「無犯罪紀錄證明書」是一項由香港警務處提供的收費服務。本處發出的「無犯罪紀錄證明書」，純粹是供有關人士申請入境簽證前往另一國家旅遊、升學或居住，或申請領養小孩之用。為任何其他目的而要求簽發「無犯罪紀錄證明書」的申請將不予以受理。"},{"pid":"dcdad141eaabe74d10870ec1684dc0ed1bf574a6","tid":1434598,"uid":265113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:23:53.000Z","msg":"銀行有compliance要check. 其他公司大部份都冇能力去check. 你話冇佢就要信你冇。都多係張申請書填有冇。"},{"pid":"6abcd074a9cb6da86e8fa87faf4717fc0dd970eb","tid":1434598,"uid":50894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2ea3cf6b767fc4ae6128199debee0b3ce78eaf43","tid":1434598,"uid":187537,"like":116,"dislike":36,"score":80,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:06:02.000Z","msg":"其實好多公司一向都要"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:24:35.000Z","msg":"我真係未遇過"},{"pid":"461ac81112e98f08d23b65ef38c1abb635ff3297","tid":1434598,"uid":221459,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:25:03.000Z","msg":"好多公司都要了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a202af0d614c3df64651cc15db4c0fc183023d2","tid":1434598,"uid":87339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d3ef6b00417ac61d06b43f6e9ed016740661a0d5","tid":1434598,"uid":39698,"like":180,"dislike":5,"score":175,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T23:02:10.000Z","msg":"據我所知做老師係要既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:26:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你以為犯罪得性罪行？"},{"pid":"f4c008f5e6d38e66045be250e1bcb17709126e38","tid":1434598,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce198e3820b37ffa64aa4c56e72a9ed2126c7e9","tid":1434598,"uid":234589,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"2ea3cf6b767fc4ae6128199debee0b3ce